--- [编译中端] 四元式流 ---
0: (=, 10, _, a)
1: (=, 20, _, b)
2: (*, b, 2, t1)
3: (+, a, t1, t2)
4: (=, t2, _, c)
5: (write, c, _, _)
6: (return, c, _, _)

